                <p>Rubbing oil on the outside of a dead hair shaft only goes so far. If your beard hair is genuinely brittle, weak, and falling out at an alarming rate, it implies the follicle factory deep inside your jaw is fundamentally starved of raw materials. You must investigate <a href="what-to-eat-for-hair-growth.php">the precise dietary macro-nutrients required to build hair</a>. Specifically, you must consume heavy internal Omegas and healthy dietary lipids, and eradicate any <a href="which-vitamin-is-essential-for-hair-growth.php">hidden vitamin deficiencies</a> destroying the keratin synthesis line.</p>

